data.description: Price Reduced! Motivated Seller! Welcome Home! Peaceful and private 1 Acre!! Walk into this to open living/dining area. Split floor plan. Spacious master bedroom with it's own fire place. Walk in shower in a huge master bath. Walk-in closets in ALL bedrooms. Granite countertops in a beautiful kitchen. Separate laundry room with great storage. The attic space is unbelievable! Walk out the back door to your own private oasis. Grill under the covered patio or lounge in the hot-tub. Walk thru the woods to a small creek that borders the property. 30 Amp Breaker for RV at 12x20 shed. Please stop by before this jewel is gone! Schedule your showing today!
